---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service | OpsHQ Digital"
  description="OpsHQ Digital terms of service for opshqdigital.com."
>
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-8">Last updated: July 2026</p>

      <div class="prose text-slate-600 leading-relaxed space-y-8">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-4">Agreement</h2>
          <p>By accessing and using opshqdigital.com ("the Site"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use the Site.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-4">Services Description</h2>
          <p>This is an informational and lead-generation website for OpsHQ Digital, a technology consulting practice. The Site provides information about our services, case studies, and a means to contact us for project inquiries.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-4">Contact Form</h2>
          <p>Submissions through our contact form are inquiries only and do not constitute a contract, agreement, or commitment to provide services. Any engagement of services will be governed by a separate agreement.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-4">Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p>All content on this Site — including text, graphics, logos, and design — is the property of OpsHQ Digital and is protected by applicable copyright laws. Case study details are shared with client permission.</p>
          <p class="mt-2">You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works from any content on this Site without prior written consent.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-4">Disclaimer</h2>
          <p>Information provided on this Site is for general informational purposes only and should not be considered professional advice. We make no guarantees of specific results from our consulting services. Past results described in case studies are specific to those projects and are not guarantees of future performance.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-4">Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p>OpsHQ Digital shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages arising from your use of the Site or reliance on any information provided herein. Our total liability to you for any claim arising from these terms shall not exceed the amount you paid us, if any, during the twelve months preceding the claim.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-4">Privacy</h2>
          <p>Your use of the Site is also governed by our <a href="/privacy/" class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-600">Privacy Policy</a>, which describes how we collect, use, and protect your information.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-4">Governing Law</h2>
          <p>These Terms of Service shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the State of Washington, without regard to its conflict of law provisions.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-4">Contact</h2>
          <p>For questions about these terms, contact us at <a href="mailto:nick@opshqdigital.com" class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-600">nick@opshqdigital.com</a>.</p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
